# User Documentation

This document explains how to use the WordPress website deployed with Inception.

---

## Website Access

The website is accessible via HTTPS only.

URL:

https://nabil.42.fr

---

## Browser

Any modern browser can be used:
- Firefox
- Chromium
- Chrome

---

## WordPress Accounts

Two accounts are created automatically:
- Administrator account
- Author account

Credentials are defined via Docker secrets during installation.

